<meta name=3D"description" content=3D"CDC has a fun new way of teaching the=
 importance of emergency preparedness. Our new graphic novel, &quot;Prepare=
dness 101: Zombie Pandemic&quot; demonstrates the importance of being prepa=
red in an entertaining way that people of all ages will enjoy. Readers foll=
ow Todd, Julie, and their dog Max as a strange new disease begins spreading=
, turning ordinary people into zombies. Stick around to the end for a surpr=
ising twist that will drive home the importance of being prepared for any e=
mergency. Included in the novel is a Preparedness Checklist so that readers=
 can get their family, workplace, or school ready before disaster strikes."=
>
