				<div class=3D"bookDetailsData collapse pt-3" id=3D"collapseDetails">
															CDC has a fun new way of teaching the importance of emergenc=
y preparedness. Our new graphic novel, "Preparedness 101: Zombie Pandemic" =
demonstrates the importance of being prepared in an entertaining way that p=
eople of all ages will enjoy. Readers follow Todd, Julie, and their dog Max=
 as a strange new disease begins spreading, turning ordinary people into zo=
mbies. Stick around to the end for a surprising twist that will drive home =
the importance of being prepared for any emergency. Included in the novel i=
s a Preparedness Checklist so that readers can get their family, workplace,=
 or school ready before disaster strikes.
